http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#lab.value: List of sports venues by capacity

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#com.value: The following is a list of sports venues, ordered by capacity; i.e. the maximum number of spectators the venue can normally accommodate. All venues with a capacity of 40,000 or more are included. Venues that are closed, defunct, or no longer serve as sports venues, are not included. Italics indicate historical regular tenant.
